Package: janet
Type: Package
Title: Joint Alignment and Nonparametric Estimation Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Péter", "Rácz", email = "petermartonracz@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes phonologically-informed pairwise word distances using
    natural class theory and Needleman-Wunsch alignment. Given a phonological
    feature matrix and a list of words, janet derives segment similarity scores,
    natural class definitions, and phonological distances between all word pairs.
    Based on Frisch, Pierrehumbert & Broe (2004) and Dawdy-Hesterberg &
    Pierrehumbert (2014).
